+++ b/Documentation/sysctl/vm.txt
@@ -19,7 +19,10 @@ files can be found in mm/swap.c.
 Currently, these files are in /proc/sys/vm:

 - admin_reserve_kbytes
+- anon_min_kbytes
 - block_dump
